```r
allDf$date <- as.Date(allDf$date) # convert date column to date format

allDf %>%
  dplyr::select(patientid,date,sampleloc,virus.bin,virus,virus_2) %>%
  distinct() %>%
  filter(!is.na(virus.bin)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = date,
           y = patientid,
           color = sampleloc,
           shape = virus.bin)) +
  geom_jitter(size = 3) +
  scale_x_date(name = \Sample date\") +
